Data Attribution:
This application uses publicly available data from the City of Calgary Open Data Portal:
- Traffic Incidents: https://data.calgary.ca/resource/35ra-9556.json  
- Traffic Cameras: https://data.calgary.ca/resource/k7p9-kppz.json

The data is provided free of charge by the City of Calgary under the Open Government License - Calgary.
More information about Calgary's Open Data can be found at: https://data.calgary.ca/

